Package net.slightlymagic.braids.util.generator

Class Summary
FindNonDirectoriesSkipDotDirectoriesGenerator This is a generator over all of the non-directories residing in a given starting directory and all subdirectories of it that do NOT start with a dot; this prevents the code from descending into .svn directories.
GeneratorFromArray<T> Creates a Generator from an array; generators are a handy substitute for passing around and creating temporary lists, collections, and arrays.
GeneratorFunctions For documentation on Java-Yield and its generators, see http://code.google.com/p/java-yield/
